Package: polyfreqs
Title: An R Package for Bayesian Population Genomics in Autopolyploids
Version: 0.9.0
Authors@R: c(person("Paul", "Blischak", , "blischak.4@osu.edu", c("aut", "cre")))
Description: polyfreqs implements a Gibbs sampler to perform Bayesian inference on biallelic SNP frequencies, genotypes and heterozygosity in a population of autopolyploids.
Depends: R (>= 3.0)
License: GPL (>=2)
LazyData: true
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
Imports: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo
Suggests: knitr, coda
VignetteBuilder: knitr
